        <p align="left" class="Stil2"><a href="bilder/ramue/ramue90g.jpg"><img src="bilder/ramue/ramue90.jpg" border="0" /></a><br>
          Fu&szlig;ball pur.</p>
        <p align="left" class="Stil2">24.08.2009 17:42 Uhr</p>       </td>
